ietnam]].\n\nAs of 2018 the district had a population of 95,360.<ref name=\"Statoids\">{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yvn.html|title=Districts of Vietnam|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=March 19, 2009}}</ref> The district covers an area of 586&nbsp;km\u00b2. The district capital lies at [[B\u1ebfn Sung]].<ref name=\"Statoids\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Districts of North Central Coast}}\n\n{{coord|19.617|N|105.533|E|type:adm2nd_region:VN|display=title}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nhu Thanh District}}\n[[Category:Districts of Thanh H\u00f3a Province]]\n{{ThanhHoa-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Expand Vietnamese|date=March 2009|Nh\u01b0 Thanh}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Nh\u01b0 Thanh District\n| settlement_type                 = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n| official_name                   = \n| other_name                      = \n| native_name                     = Huy\u1ec7n Nh\u01b0 Thanh\n| nickname                        = \n| motto                           = \n| image_skyline                   = \n| imagesize                       = \n| image_caption                   = \n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_size                       = \n| image_shield                    = \n| shield_size                     = \n| image_blank_emblem              = \n| blank_emblem_size               = \n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| image_map1                      = \n| mapsize1                        = \n| map_caption1                    = \n| pushpin_map                     = \n| pushpin_label_position          = \n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|Vietnam}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[Regions of Vietnam|Region]]\n| subdivision_name1               = [[North Central Coast]]\n| subdivision_type2              