e/Portugal}}\n* [https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-17758217 Portugal profile] from the [[BBC News]]\n* [http://www.theportugalnews.com/ National English language newspaper]\n* {{Wikiatlas|Portugal}}\n* {{osmrelation-inline|295480}}\n* [http://www.winesofportugal.info/?market=2 National Wine Website]\n* [https://www.loc.gov/rr/rarebook/coll/portpam.html Portuguese Pamphlets Collection] From the [https://www.loc.gov/rr/rarebook/ Rare Book and Special Collections Division at the Library of Congress]\n\n; Government\n* [http://www.portugal.gov.pt/en.aspx Official Portuguese Government website] {{in lang|en|pt}}\n* [http://www.en.parlamento.pt/ Official Parliament website]\n;Trade\n* [http://wits.worldbank.org/CountryProfile/en/Country/PRT/Year/2012/Summary World Bank Summary Trade Statistics Portugal]\n; Travel\n* [https://www.visitportugal.com/en Official Travel and Tourism office website]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170724142744/http://www.turismodeportugal.pt/english/TurismodeportugalIP/Pages/TurismodePortugalIP.aspx Official Portuguese Government Travel/media website]\n* [http://www.portugalgolfbooking.com/ Official Portuguese Golf Travel/media website]\n\n{{Portugal topics|state=collapsed}}\n{{Portugal geography|the country}}\n{{navboxes |title=Articles related to Portugal| list  =\n{{Sovereign states of Europe}}\n{{Members of the European Union (EU)}}\n{{Council of Europe}}\n{{North Atlantic Treaty Organisation (NATO)}}\n{{Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development}}\n{{Community of Portuguese Language Countries (CPLP)|state=collapsed}}\n{{World Trade Organization}}\n{{Portuguese overseas empire}}\n{{National personifications}}\n}}\n{{Coord|38|42|N|9|11|W|type:country|display=title}}{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Portugal| ]]<!--please leave the empty space as standard-->\n[[Category:Iberian Peninsula]]\n[[Category:Member states of NATO]]\n[[Category:Member states of the Community of Portuguese Language Countries]]\n[[Category:Member s